            <title>[PIG-3198] Let users use any function from PigType -&gt; PigType as if it were builtlin</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3198</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This idea is an extension of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2643&quot; title=&quot;Use bytecode generation to make a performance replacement for InvokeForLong, InvokeForString, etc&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-2643&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-2643&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Ideally, someone should be able to call any function currently registered in Pig as if it were builtin.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12633009">PIG-3198</key>
            <summary>Let users use any function from PigType -&gt; PigType as if it were builtlin</summary>
